             was indicted for <rs id="t17930529-60-off331" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17930529-60-off331" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17930529-60-off331" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17930529-60-cd332" type="crimeDate">27th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930529-60-off331 t17930529-60-cd332"></join>, a wooden Cask, value 8 d. and two hundred and two pounds weight of salted butter, value 6 l.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17930529-60-victim766" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Todd
                  <interp inst="t17930529-60-victim766" type="surname" value="Todd"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17930529-60-victim766" type="given" value="John"></interp>
