                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930529-60-defend764 t17930529-60-punish336"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury before Mr. COMMON SERJEANT.</p>
